00:10:39.770 --> 00:10:41.550 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:42.640 align:middle line:90%
>> Nature tends not to--

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:43.440 align:middle line:90%
>> Not to do that.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.345 align:middle line:90%
Not to do that.

00:10:44.345 --> 00:10:44.810 align:middle line:90%
>> Absolutely.

