00:10:50.030 --> 00:10:50.830 align:middle line:90%
>> I agree.

00:10:50.830 --> 00:10:51.630 align:middle line:90%
>> I agree.

00:10:51.630 --> 00:10:53.840 align:middle line:84%
>> But one thing is, when
